# Launching OpenSquirrel

- When asked to launch or open the app for manual inspection, do not use `cargo run` directly.
- Use `scripts/launch-opensquirrel-app.sh` so the app opens as `dist/OpenSquirrel.app` with the real `OpenSquirrel.icns` icon.
- This launcher should be treated as the default production-style launch path for this project.
- Use `cargo test` or `cargo build` normally for verification, but use the launcher script for actual app opening.
- If needed, set `OPEN_SQUIRREL_PROFILE=debug` before running the script; otherwise it should use `release`.
